    • Constructor Detail

      • ImmutableEvent

        public ImmutableEvent(String agentId,
                      String system,
                      String type,
                      String globalEventId,
                      String parentEventId,
                      String marker,
                      EventProperties properties)
        Create an new Event: the id and the timestamp are set automatically by using UUID.randomUUID() and new Date.
        Parameters:
        agentId - The id of the agent recording this Event.
        system - The system recording this Event.
        type - The Event type.
        globalEventId - The global Event id.
        parentEventId - The parent Event id.
        marker - The marker.
        properties - The properties.
